com.ib.client

Class Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ib.client.Builder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.DataOutput, java.io.ObjectOutput, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class Builder
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.ObjectOutput
    This class is used to build messages so the entire message can be sent to the socket in a single write.
